title: A familiar nemesis, turnovers, returns for Georgia Tech -  The Atlanta Journal Constitution
content: A familiar nemesis, turnovers, returns for Georgia Tech   The Atlanta Journal Constitution
description: Georgia Tech has shown this season that it can play without giving the ball away. In 24 games this season, the Yellow Jackets have had seven games in which they turned the ball over 10 times or fewer, most recently in their upset of Florida State on Jan. 26 (nine turnovers).
